  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7487577/" class="title-link">坚持作死，就一定会死——读《日本政治史》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7487577"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2660313/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2660313-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2660313/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">nile</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-06-01"
      class="main-meta">2015-06-01 19:58:44</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7487577_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  1941年中，法国沦陷已经有一年。6月，德军痛揍俄熊，开始了东进冒险。7月底，日军南进法属印度支那，一方面试图趁法国之危接管其殖民地；一方面从侧面围堵蒋政权，威胁滇缅公路；另一方面也是试探美国底线。虽然此时“日美必有一战”的舆论在日本国内甚嚣尘上，但从天皇到首相...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7487577_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7487577_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





